#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:1
msgid "General Preferences in Krita."
msgstr "Krita 的一般偏好設定。"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:17
msgid "General Settings"
msgstr "「一般」設定"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:19
msgid ""
"You can access the General Category of the preferences by first going to :"
"menuselection:`Settings --> Configure Krita...` menu item."
msgstr ""
"Krita 的一般設定中包含了游標、視窗、工具、檔案和一些重要的選項。您可以通過"
"\\ :menuselection:`「設定」 --> 「設定 Krita…」` 進入設定。"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:24
msgid "Cursor Settings"
msgstr "游標設定"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:26
msgid "Customize the drawing cursor here:"
msgstr "您可以在這裡自訂繪圖游標："

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:29
msgid "Cursor Shape"
msgstr "游標形狀"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:31
msgid ""
"Select a cursor shape to use while the brush tools are used. This cursor "
"will always be visible on the canvas. It is usually set to a type exactly "
"where your pen nib is at. The available cursor types are shown below."
msgstr ""
"選擇於使用筆刷工具時顯示的游標形狀，當游標移動到畫布視圖上就會以所選樣式一直"
"顯示在筆尖位置，可用的游標形狀如下所示。"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:36
msgid "Tool Icon"
msgstr "工具圖示"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:34
msgid "Shows the currently selected tool icon, even for the freehand brush."
msgstr "顯示當前工具圖示，在使用筆刷工具時也顯示筆刷圖示。"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:41
msgid "Arrow"
msgstr "箭頭"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:39
msgid "Shows a generic cursor."
msgstr "顯示一般箭頭游標。"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:46
msgid "Crosshair"
msgstr "十字線"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:44
msgid "Shows a precision reticule."
msgstr "顯示準星狀十字線。"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:51
msgid "Small circle"
msgstr "小圓圈"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:49
msgid "Shows a small white dot with a black outline."
msgstr "顯示一個白底黑線小圓圈。"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:56
msgid "No Cursor"
msgstr "沒有游標"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:54
msgid "Show no cursor, useful for tablet-monitors."
msgstr "不顯示游標，可用於平板電腦。"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:61
msgid "Triangle Right-Handed."
msgstr "三角形（慣用右手）。"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:59
msgid "Gives a small white triangle with a black border."
msgstr "顯示一個白底黑邊箭頭，箭頭朝右手使用者習慣的方向。"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:66
msgid "Triangle Left-Handed."
msgstr "三角形（慣用左手）。"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:64
msgid "Same as above but mirrored."
msgstr "與上面相同，但箭頭朝左手使用者習慣的方向。"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:71
msgid "Black Pixel"
msgstr "黑色像素"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:69
msgid "Gives a single black pixel."
msgstr "僅顯示一個黑色像素。"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:77
msgid "White Pixel"
msgstr "白色像素"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:74
msgid "Gives a single white pixel."
msgstr "僅顯示一個白色像素。"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:80
msgid "Outline Shape"
msgstr "輪廓形狀"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:82
msgid ""
"Select an outline shape to use while the brush tools are used. This cursor "
"shape will optionally show in the middle of a painting stroke as well. The "
"available outline shape types are shown below. (pictures will come soon)"
msgstr ""
"選取筆刷工具使用時要顯示的輪廓形狀。您可選擇是否在繪圖時持續顯示輪廓，可用的"
"輪廓形狀如下所示。（目前無說明圖片）"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:84
msgid "No Outline"
msgstr "不顯示輪廓"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:85
msgid "Turns the outline off."
msgstr "不顯示筆刷輪廓。"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:86
msgid "Circle Outline"
msgstr "圓形輪廓"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:87
msgid "Gives a circular outline approximating the brush size."
msgstr "顯示大約符合筆刷尺寸的圓形輪廓。"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:88
msgid "Preview Outline"
msgstr "預覽輪廓"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:89
msgid "Gives an outline based on the actual shape of the brush."
msgstr "根據筆刷實際的形狀顯示輪廓。"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:93
msgid "Tilt Outline"
msgstr "傾斜度輪廓"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:91
msgid "Gives a circular outline with a tilt-indicator."
msgstr "顯示帶有筆刷傾斜度指示的圓形輪廓。"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:96
msgid "While Painting..."
msgstr "繪圖的時候…"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:103
msgid "Show Outline"
msgstr "顯示輪廓"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:99
msgid ""
"This option when selected will show the brush outline while a stroke is "
"being made. If unchecked the brush outline will not appear during stroke "
"making, it will show up only after the brush stroke is finished. This option "
"works only when Brush Outline is selected as the Cursor Shape."
msgstr ""
"勾選這個項目時，在筆刷進行繪圖當中會持續顯示輪廓；而不勾選這個項目的狀況下，"
"繪圖進行中不會顯示輪廓，僅在下筆之前和筆刷完成繪圖後才會顯示輪廓。這個選項只"
"有在啟用「筆刷輪廓」時才有作用。"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:103
msgid "Used to be called \"Show Outline When Painting\"."
msgstr "曾經被稱為「繪畫時顯示輪廓」。"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:106
msgid "Use effective outline size"
msgstr "使用有效的輪廓大小"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:106
msgid ""
"This makes sure that the outline size will always be the maximum possible "
"brush diameter, and not the current one as affected by sensors such as "
"pressure. This makes the cursor a little less noisy to use."
msgstr ""
"勾選這個功能時，筆刷輪廓的大小會按照數位板感壓筆壓力大小相應變化。在不勾選的"
"狀況下，筆刷輪廓會保持它的大小以減少干擾。"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:110
msgid "Cursor Color:"
msgstr "游標顏色："

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:109
msgid ""
"The default cursor color. This is mixed with the canvas image so that it "
"will usually have a contrasting color, but sometimes this mixing does not "
"work. This is usually due driver problems. When that happens, you can "
"configure a more pleasant color here."
msgstr ""
"預設的游標顏色，這顏色會在畫布上以對比色顯示，儘可能做到在各種顏色下游標依然"
"清晰可辨。但有時在某些顏色下無法看清，這可能是顯示器驅動程式造成的問題，這時"
"您可換用另一個顏色來試試看效果是否有改善。"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:115
msgid "Window Settings"
msgstr "視窗設定"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:117
msgid "Multiple Document Mode"
msgstr "多檔案模式"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:118
msgid ""
"This can be either tabbed like :program:`GIMP` or :program:`Paint Tool SAI`, "
"or sub windows, like :program:`Photoshop`."
msgstr ""
"這裡可依喜好設定為類似 :program:`GIMP` 或 :program:`Paint Tool SAI` 那樣將每"
"個開啟的檔案在畫布視圖上以「分頁」方式呈現；也可設定為 :program:`PhotoShop` "
"那樣將每個開啟的檔案以「子視窗」呈現。"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:119
msgid "Background image"
msgstr "背景影像"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:120
msgid "Allows you to set a picture background for sub window mode."
msgstr ""
"這功能可讓您選取並自訂子視窗模式的背景影像，若不想再使用背景影像時可按「清"
"除」移除。"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:121
msgid "Window Background"
msgstr "視窗背景色彩"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:122
msgid "Set the color of the sub window canvas area."
msgstr "自訂子視窗模式下畫布區域的色彩。"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:126
msgid "Use Custom Interface Font"
msgstr "自訂使用者介面字型"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:124
msgid ""
"This allows you to tweak the interface font and the size. Requires a restart."
msgstr "這裡可自訂使用者介面字型與字體大小。變更之後需要重新啟動 Krita。"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:128
msgid "Don't show contents when moving sub-windows"
msgstr "移動子視窗時不顯示內容"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:129
msgid ""
"This gives an outline when moving windows to work around ugly glitches with "
"certain graphics-cards."
msgstr ""
"移動子視窗時只顯示輪廓。在比較差的顯卡驅動程式下可試著使用這項目以改善顯示。"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:130
msgid "Show on-canvas popup messages"
msgstr "在畫布上顯示浮動訊息"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:131
msgid ""
"Whether you want to see the on-canvas pop-up messages that tell you whether "
"you are in tabbed mode, rotating the canvas, or mirroring it."
msgstr ""
"選擇是否在畫布上浮動顯示當前您使用的是何種功能選項模式、旋轉畫布或鏡像。"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:132
msgid "Enable Hi-DPI support"
msgstr "啟用高解析度螢幕（Hi-DPI ）支援"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:133
msgid ""
"Attempt to use the Hi-DPI support. It is an option because we are still "
"experiencing bugs on Windows."
msgstr ""
"嘗試使用 Hi-DPI 支援。這只是個選項，因為在 Windows 系統上此功能尚未成熟依然有"
"介面顯示過大的錯誤發生。"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:135
msgid "(Hi-DPI) Enable fractional scale factor"
msgstr "啟用非整數比例縮放（Hi-DPI）"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:135
msgid ""
"Allow the Hi-DPI support to use fractional (not multiples of 100%) display "
"scaling. If you use a fractional display scaling, this option can make the "
"interface of Krita match the interface size of the rest of your system, but "
"it may cause some visual artifacts."
msgstr ""
"允許在高解析支援模式下使用非整數倍數（不是 100% 的整數倍數）顯示縮放。若您的"
"系統使用了非整數倍數縮放，這個選項可讓 Krita 的介面與系統互相配合，但可能因此"
"造成一些顯示時不自然的問題。"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:142
msgid "Allow only one instance of Krita"
msgstr "只允許一個 Krita 實例執行"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:138
msgid ""
"An instance is a single entry in your system's task manager. Turning this "
"option makes sure that Krita will check if there's an instance of Krita open "
"already when you instruct it to open new documents, and then have your "
"documents opened in that single instance. There's some obscure uses to "
"allowing multiple instances, but if you can't think of any, just keep this "
"option on."
msgstr ""
"實例是系統任務管理員中的單個處理程序。打開此選項可確保在點開 Krita 格式檔案"
"時，先檢查是否有 Krita 處理程序已經‎‎打開，若有的話就使用這個實例來打開檔案。在"
"某些比較少見的工作流程可能會需要使用多個 Krita 實例，但若您不知可以做何種用途"
"的話請將這個項目勾選即可。"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:142
msgid ""
"Since Krita 5.0 this has been deprecated, as it now uses a SQLite database "
"for handling the resources, and this cannot be managed by multiple instances."
msgstr ""
"從 Krita 5.0 開始，這個功能已廢棄不用。因為新版 Krita 改用了 SQLite 資料庫來"
"管理資源，而且工作上也無法再支援多個實例。"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:147
msgid "Tools Settings"
msgstr "工具設定"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:150
msgid "Tool Options Location"
msgstr "工具選項位置"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:152
msgid "In docker (default)"
msgstr "在工具面版中（預設）"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:153
msgid "Gives you the tool options in a docker."
msgstr "工具選項會顯示在一個單獨的面版中，這是預設。"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:155
msgid "In toolbar"
msgstr "在工具列內"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:155
msgid ""
"Gives you the tool options in the toolbar, next to the brush settings. You "
"can open it with the :kbd:`\\\\` key."
msgstr ""
"使用此選項的話，工具選項會顯示在工具列上，點一下即可顯示，也可用 :kbd:`\\\\` "
"快捷鍵叫出。"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:158
msgid "Brush Flow Mode"
msgstr "筆刷流量模式"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:158
msgid ""
"In Krita 4.2 the behavior of flow in combination with opacity was changed. "
"This allows you to turn it back to the 4.1 behavior. This will however be "
"removed in future versions."
msgstr ""
"Krita 4.2 版改變了筆刷在使用流量和不透明度的演算法，這選項允許您切換到舊版模"
"式，但這最後也將會在未來的版本中移除。"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:161
msgid "Switch Control/Alt Selection Modifiers"
msgstr "在使用選取區域工具時交換 Ctrl 與 Alt 組合鍵的作用"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:161
msgid ""
"This switches the function of the :kbd:`Ctrl` and :kbd:`Alt` keys when "
"modifying selections. Useful for those used to Gimp instead of Photoshop, or "
"Lefties without a right :kbd:`Alt` key on their keyboard."
msgstr ""
"選用這個功能後，會交換 :kbd:`Ctrl` 和 :kbd:`Alt` 鍵在修改選取區域時的組合鍵。"
"此功能是專為習慣 Gimp 而不是 PhotoShop 組合鍵的人，或鍵盤右邊沒有 :kbd:`Alt` "
"鍵的左撇子畫家而準備的。"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:168
msgid "Enable Touch painting"
msgstr "啟用以手指在觸控螢幕上繪畫"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:164
msgid ""
"This allows finger painting with capacitive screens. Some devices have both "
"capacitive touch and a stylus, and then this can interfere. In that case, "
"just toggle this."
msgstr ""
"這功能啟用後，可用手指在電容觸控螢幕上繪圖。有些螢幕同時擁有電容觸控與繪數位"
"板功能，這可能會干擾感壓筆的繪圖輸入，此時請關閉這個功能。"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:168
msgid ""
"When this is disabled, panning the canvas can be done with by dragging a "
"single finger over the canvas, while when enabled, panning will only be done "
"by dragging three fingers."
msgstr ""
"停用此選項後可使用單指手勢來平移畫布；啟用後則需用三指手勢才能平移畫布。"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:171
msgid "Activate transform tool after pasting"
msgstr "在貼上後自動切換到變形工具"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:171
msgid ""
"A convenience feature. When enabling this, the transform tool will activate "
"after pasting for quick moving or rotating."
msgstr ""
"這是個方便的功能，在啟用此選項的狀態下，貼上之後會自動切換到變形工具以快速移"
"動或旋轉。"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:174
msgid "Enable Touch Rotation"
msgstr "啟用觸控螢幕旋轉手勢"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:174
msgid ""
"Without this, gestures on the canvas only allow zoom and pan, with this "
"turned on, the two-finger gesture also allows to rotate."
msgstr ""
"不勾選此功能時，觸控手勢只能縮放與平移畫布視圖。勾選這項目後，兩指手勢還能執"
"行旋轉畫布視圖。"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:197
msgid "Kinetic Scrolling (Needs Restart)"
msgstr "拖曳捲動（需要重啟程式）"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:177
msgid "This enables kinetic scrolling for scrollable areas."
msgstr ""
"在所有可捲動面板啟用「拖曳捲動」的功能，預設是使用按下滑鼠中鍵的方式拖動，效"
"果類似在觸控螢幕以指尖滑動。"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:182
msgid ""
"Kinetic scrolling on the brush chooser drop-down with activation mode set "
"to :guilabel:`On Click Drag`, with this disabled all of these clicks would "
"lead to a brush being selected regardless of drag motion."
msgstr ""
"在啟用\\ :guilabel:`點擊並拖曳捲動`\\ 的狀態時，只要按住滑鼠左鍵不放，面板上"
"的游標即變成拖動圖示，不會因此誤選列表中的內容。"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:192
msgid "Activation"
msgstr "拖動方式"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:185
msgid "How it is activated."
msgstr "選擇拖曳捲動啟用的方式。"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:187
msgid "On Middle-Click Drag"
msgstr "按住中間鍵拖曳捲動"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:188
msgid "Will activate when using the middle mouse button."
msgstr "在可捲動面板上按住滑鼠中鍵（或滾輪）不放時啟用拖曳捲動。"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:189
msgid "On Touch Drag"
msgstr "以觸控螢幕拖曳捲動"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:190
msgid "Will activate if it can recognize a touch event. May not always work."
msgstr ""
"在觸控螢幕中於可捲動面板偵測到動作時啟用，但這個選項並非總是能夠正常工作。"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:192
msgid "On Click Drag"
msgstr "點擊並拖曳捲動"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:192
msgid "Will activate when it can recognize a click event, will always work."
msgstr "在可捲動面板上按住滑鼠左鍵時拖曳捲動，這個選項一定可以正常操作。"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:194
msgid "Sensitivity"
msgstr "靈敏度"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:195
msgid ""
"How quickly the feature activates, this effective determines the length of "
"the drag."
msgstr "此設定影響拖曳被啟動的速度以及拖曳的有效距離。"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:197
msgid "Hide Scrollbar"
msgstr "啟用拖曳捲動時，隱藏工具面板的捲動軸（需要重啟程式）"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:197
msgid "Whether to show scrollbars when doing this."
msgstr "在啟用拖曳捲動的功能時，是否隱藏工具面板之捲動軸。"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:202
msgid "File Handling"
msgstr "檔案處理"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:206
msgid "Enable Autosaving"
msgstr "啟用自動儲存"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:207
msgid "Determines whether Krita should periodically autosave."
msgstr "啟用此選項時，Krita 將每隔一段時間自動儲存。"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:208
msgid "Autosave Every"
msgstr "自動儲存間隔"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:209
msgid ""
"Here the user can specify how often Krita should autosave the file, you can "
"tick the checkbox to turn it off. For Windows these files are saved in the ``"
"%TEMP%`` directory. If you are on Linux it is stored in :file:`/"
"home/'username'`."
msgstr ""
"指定每隔多長的時間後進行一次自動儲存，取消勾選「啟用自動儲存」將會關閉此功"
"能。 Windows 系統自動儲存的檔案位於\\ ``%TEMP%``\\ 目錄，Linux 系統則儲存的檔"
"案在\\ :file:`/home/'username'` \\目錄。"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:210
msgid "Unnamed autosave files are hidden by default"
msgstr "預設隱藏未命名的自動儲存檔案"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:211
msgid ""
"This determines whether the filename of autosaves has a period prepended to "
"the name. On Linux and macOS this is a technique to ensure the file is "
"hidden by default."
msgstr ""
"勾選這項目時，自動儲存的檔案名稱會插入一個半形句點，在 Linux 和 MacOS 系統下"
"會預設將這種檔案指定為隱藏檔。"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:212
msgid "Create Backup File"
msgstr "儲存時建立備份檔案"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:213
msgid ""
"When selected Krita will, upon save, rename the original file as a backup "
"file and save the current image to the original name. The result is that you "
"will have saved the image, and there will be a copy of the image that is "
"saved separately as a backup. This is useful in case of crashes during saves."
msgstr ""
"選用這功能時，Krita 會在儲存時給原始檔案重新命名，並且將目前影像儲存為原始檔"
"名。這表示您可以儲存一個影像檔案的同時另外保存備份檔，因為若不幸出現當機問題"
"時，您還能從備份檔中復原當機前的工作進度。"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:222
msgid "Backup File Location"
msgstr "備份檔案位置"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:215
msgid "The default location these backups should be stored."
msgstr "儲存這些備份檔案的預設目錄。"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:217
msgid "Same Folder as Original File"
msgstr "與原始檔案相同資料夾"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:218
msgid "Store the file in the same folder as the original file was stored."
msgstr "將備份檔案儲存在原始檔同一個目錄裡。"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:219
msgid "User Folder"
msgstr "使用者資料夾"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:220
msgid ""
"This is the main folder of your computer. On Linux and macOS this is the "
"'Home' folder, on Windows, the :file:`c:\\Users\\YOUR_USER_NAME` folder "
"(where ``YOUR_USER_NAME`` is your windows username)."
msgstr ""
"這是您電腦上的主資料夾。在 Linux 與 MacOS 系統中相當於「Home」用戶資料夾。在 "
"Windows 系統則是\\ :file:`c:\\\\Users\\\\YOUR_USER_NAME`\\ 資料夾（其中\\ "
"``YOUR_USER_NAME``\\ 是您在 Windows 系統下使用的名稱）。"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:222
msgid "Temporary File Folder"
msgstr "暫存位置"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:222
msgid ""
"This stored the file in the temp folder. Temp folders are special folders of "
"which the contents are emptied when you shut down your computer. If you "
"don't particularly care about your backup files and want them to be "
"'cleaned' automatically, this is the best place. If you want your backup "
"files to be kept indefinitely, this is a wrong choice."
msgstr ""
"使用這個選項會將備份檔放到暫存資料夾。暫存資料夾是個在關閉電腦時會清空內容的"
"特殊目錄，如果您不特別需要保存備份檔案並且希望讓電腦自動清理，那可以選擇將備"
"份檔案放在這裡；反之若您希望無限期保存備份檔案，那麼設定在這個暫存資料夾則不"
"是個好決定。"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:224
msgid "Backup File Suffix"
msgstr "備份檔案後綴"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:225
msgid ""
"The suffix that will be placed after the full filename. ``filename.kra`` "
"will then be saved as ``filename.kra~``, ensuring the files won't show up in "
"Krita's open file dialog."
msgstr ""
"在備份檔名添加後綴符號。例如使用預設的 ``~`` 符號時， ``filename.kra`` 將被儲"
"存為 ``filename.kra~`` ，以確保這些檔案不會出現在 Krita 開啟檔案的對話視窗中"
"造成混淆。"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:226
msgid "Number of Backup Files Kept"
msgstr "保留的備份檔案數目"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:227
msgid ""
"Number of backup files Krita keeps, by default this is only one, but this "
"can be up to 99. Krita will then number the backup files."
msgstr ""
"指定 Krita 保留備份檔案的數量，預設情況下僅有 1 個，但您最多可以指定 99 個備"
"份檔，Krita 會自動給檔案加上編號。"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:228
msgid "Compress ``\\*.kra`` files more (slows loading/saving)"
msgstr "提高 .kra 檔案的壓縮率（載入及儲存的速度會變慢）"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:229
msgid ""
"This increases the ZIP compression on the saved Krita files, which makes "
"them lighter on disk, but this takes longer to load."
msgstr ""
"這會增加保存的 Krita 檔案的 ZIP 壓縮率，使它們佔用較少的硬碟空間，但開啟時間"
"會更長。"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:230
msgid "Use Zip64"
msgstr "使用 Zip64"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:231
msgid ""
"KRA files are ZIP files. Zip64 allows you to make really large image files "
"(which is useful for animation), however, not all ZIP file programs can read "
"Zip64, including older versions of Krita."
msgstr ""
"KRA 檔案本身其實是 ZIP 格式檔案。Zip64 的擴充格式可以支援比較大的影像檔案（例"
"如動畫），但相對的並非所有 ZIP 檔案軟體都可以開啟 Zip64 格式壓縮檔，舊版的 "
"Krita 也不支援這種格式。"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:234
msgid "Trim Files before Saving"
msgstr "儲存前裁剪檔案"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:233
msgid ""
"Normally, Krita will always keep pixels outside the visible canvas area and "
"save that. With this option turned on, Krita will first :ref:`crop "
"<crop_tool>` all the layers to the canvas-area and then save it."
msgstr ""
"通常 Krita 儲存時會將所有可見像素保留在畫布及畫布以外的區域。啟用這個選項後，"
"Krita 會先以 \\ :ref:`修剪至影像大小 <crop_tool>`\\ 將所有圖層裁剪到僅有畫布"
"區域再進行儲存。"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:239
msgid "Miscellaneous"
msgstr "其它"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:250
msgid "When Krita starts"
msgstr "當 Krita 啟動時"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:242
msgid ""
"This is the option for handling :ref:`user sessions <working_sessions>`. It "
"has the following options:"
msgstr ""
"這個是在 Krita 啟動時如何處理\\ :ref:`使用者工作階段 <working_sessions>`\\ 的"
"選項，它有以下項目可用："

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:244
msgid "Open Default Window"
msgstr "開啟預設視窗"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:245
msgid "This opens the regular empty window with the last used workspace."
msgstr "這將打開帶有上次使用的工作區設定的空白視窗。"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:246
msgid "Load Previous Session"
msgstr "載入上一次工作階段"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:247
msgid ""
"Load the last opened session. If you have :guilabel:`Save session when Krita "
"closes` toggled, this becomes the last files you had open and the like."
msgstr ""
"載入上一次的工作階段。若您勾選了\\ :guilabel:`關閉 Krita 時儲存工作階段`\\ 項"
"目，Krita 會自動記下工作階段的最後狀態，例如打開的檔案和視窗佈局。"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:249
msgid "Show Session Manager"
msgstr "顯示工作階段管理器"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:249
msgid "Show the session manager directly, so you can pick a session."
msgstr "打開 Krita 時顯示「工作階段管理器」，讓您選擇要載入的工作階段。"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:254
msgid "Save session when Krita closes"
msgstr "關閉 Krita 時儲存工作階段"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:253
msgid ""
"Save the current open windows, documents and the like into the current "
"session when closing Krita, so you can resume where you left off."
msgstr ""
"在關閉 Krita 時將當前打開的視窗、檔案保存到當前工作階段中，以便下次開啟 "
"Krita 時選取要加載的工作階段。"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:256
msgid "Upon importing Images as Layers, convert to the image color space."
msgstr "匯入影像為圖層時，將其轉換為目標影像的色彩空間。"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:257
msgid ""
"This makes sure that layers are the same color space as the image, necessary "
"for saving to PSD."
msgstr ""
"這功能可確保圖層與影像擁有相同的色彩空間，這選項是儲存 PSD 格式檔案時所必須"
"的。"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:258
msgid "Undo Stack Size"
msgstr "復原次數上限"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:259
msgid ""
"This is the number of undo commands Krita remembers. You can set the value "
"to 0 for unlimited undo commands."
msgstr "這是 Krita 可復原紀錄的數量，將其設定為 0 即可無限制復原次數。"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:264
msgid "Enable Logging For Bug Reports"
msgstr "啟用供錯誤報告用的紀錄"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:261
msgid ""
"This controls whether Krita keeps a log of the important actions, which can "
"then be attached to a bug report. You can view the log itself via :"
"menuselection:`Help --> Show Krita Log for Bug Reports`, and the log itself "
"is stored in the shared application settings."
msgstr ""
"此選項啟用時 Krita 會將程式的重要操作紀錄到日誌檔中，以便於需要回報程式錯誤時"
"附加到報告作為判斷線索。您可以通過\\ :menuselection:`說明 --> 顯示要用於錯誤"
"報告的 Krita 紀錄`\\ 來察看 Krita 日誌，這個日誌檔會儲存在作業系統的應用程式"
"共享設定目錄。"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:265
msgid ""
"Krita does not automatically transfer data anywhere. The log needs to be "
"uploaded by users themselves if necessary."
msgstr ""
"Krita 不會自動將錯誤報告上傳到任何地方。您需要手動將日誌內容附加到程式錯誤報"
"告中。"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:271
msgid "Hide splash screen on startup."
msgstr "啟動時隱藏歡迎畫面。"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:267
msgid ""
"This'll hide the splash screen automatically once Krita is fully loaded."
msgstr "在 Krita 完成啟動後自動關閉歡迎畫面。"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:271
msgid ""
"Deprecated because Krita now has a welcome widget when no canvas is open."
msgstr "此選項在新版中已不存在。新版 Krita 會在啟動完成後直接顯示歡迎畫面。"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:273
msgid "Enable Native File Dialog"
msgstr "啟用系統原生「開啟」/「儲存」檔案對話框"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:274
msgid ""
"This allows you to use the system file dialog. Turned off by default, "
"because we cannot seem to get native file dialogues 100% bug free."
msgstr ""
"勾選這個項目後 Krita 會嘗試使用作業系統原生檔案對話視窗。這功能不一定 100% 正"
"常工作，若您遇到問題時請取消勾選這個項目。"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:275
msgid "Maximum brush size"
msgstr "筆刷最大大小"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:276
msgid ""
"This allows you to set the maximum brush size to a size of up to 10,000 "
"pixels. Do be careful with using this, as a 10,000 pixel size can very "
"quickly be a full gigabyte of data being manipulated, per dab. In other "
"words, this might be slow."
msgstr ""
"這功能可以指定筆刷大小上限，最高可設定為 10,000 像素的大小。但 10,000 這樣多"
"的像素每一筆畫都會產生大約 1GB 的資料量，這將造成系統緩慢，因此請小心使用。"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:281
msgid "Recalculate animation cache in background."
msgstr "在背景計算動畫快取。"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:278
msgid "Krita will recalculate the cache when you're not doing anything."
msgstr "Krita 會在您沒有執行任何動作時於背景生成動畫快取。"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:282
msgid ""
"This is now in the :ref:`performance_settings` under :guilabel:`Animation "
"Cache`."
msgstr ""
"這選項已移動到\\ :ref:`performance_settings`\\ 項目下的\\ :guilabel:`「動畫快"
"取」`\\ 中。"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:286
msgid "Automatically Pin New layers To Timeline."
msgstr "自動釘選新圖層至時間軸。"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:284
msgid ""
"Used with the :ref:`timeline_docker`, this will pin all animation layers to "
"the timeline automatically. Depending on your workflow, this can be quite "
"intense, so hence the option to turn it off."
msgstr ""
"與\\ :ref:`timeline_docker`\\ 配合使用，選用這功能後會將所有動畫圖層自動固定"
"到時間軸面板。在某些工作流程下這可能會大量佔用系統資源造成操作緩慢，您可以選"
"擇將此功能關閉。"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:291
msgid "Adapt playback range to key frames."
msgstr "將重播範圍調整至關鍵影格。"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:289
msgid ""
"This option decides whether adding key frames outside the current playback "
"range automatically extends the playback range or not."
msgstr ""
"鉤選這個項目後，在當前播放範圍之外增加新的關鍵影格時，Krita 會自動延長播放範"
"圍。"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:298
msgid "Font DPI Workaround"
msgstr "字形 DPI 應急修正方法"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:294
msgid ""
"We had a bug in Krita 4.x where the DPI of the display affected the DPI of "
"the text."
msgstr ""
"Krita 4.x 中有一個程式錯誤，它會造成顯示器的 DPI 設定影響文字的 DPI 。此錯誤"
"已在新版 Krita 獲得解決，但在開啟舊版 Krita 所儲存的檔案時，可能需要轉換字體 "
"DPI 以保持字體的一致性。"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:296
msgid ""
"Now when loading a file created in Krita 4.4 we convert its font sizes using "
"the DPI of the display and bake this new value into the file. The user can "
"override this behavior by selecting another DPI in here. Setting this value "
"to 72 DPI will effectively disable any scaling."
msgstr ""
"新版 Krita 在載入 4.4 版所建立的檔案時，我們使用 DISP 的 DPI 來轉換其字體大"
"小，並將此新值轉移到檔案中。您可以通過在這裡設定另一個DPI來覆寫此行為。若將此"
"值設置為 72 dpi 將不進行任何縮放。"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:303
msgid "Resources"
msgstr "資源"

#: ../../reference_manual/preferences/general_settings.rst:305
msgid "For determining the location of the resource folder and the cache."
msgstr "用以決定資源檔案目錄和快取的位置。"

